The composition of two pullback functors on presheaves of modules `pullback œÜ ‚ãô pullback œà` identifies to the pullback of the composition. We show compatibilites for these isomorphisms: they are deduced from similar identifies for pushforward (in which case they are `rfl`).
 
---

- [x] depends on: #17366
